{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script scans the current project file for broken JSFX references and prompts for the new location of each unique missing JSFX found.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A fixed copy of the project file is created (OriginalName-jsfix.RPP).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script supports JSFX located either in the resource folder or in the project directory.\par}
