{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Notes that intersect the cutting line will be split at the position of intersection.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If snap-to-grid is enabled, the notes will be split at the grid.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Instructions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To use, position mouse in the 'notes' area of the piano roll, press the shortcut key once, and then move the mouse to draw the cutting line.\par}
